The '''Galactic Registry''' was a listing of all known [[Planet/Legends|planets]] and species in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. Created under the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], [[Pzob/Legends|Pzob's]] Registry number was 011-733-800-022. The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] removed [[Alzoc III/Legends|Alzoc III]] from the registry.

